ata.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CYEV/111%2c%e5%98%89%e5%b0%8f%2c332%2c20220419%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CYEV,111,嘉小,332,20220419,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"嘉小","JNO":"332","JDATE":"20220419","JTITLE":"侵權行為損害賠償(交通)"}